snippet.title: F1 2018 | Making Headlines | Career Developer Diary 1 [UK]
snippet.description:
Speak to the press and 'Make Headlines' in F1 2018 - watch Game Director Lee Mather show you how in our brand new Developer Diary.

Learn more here: http://blog.codemasters.com/f1/07/speak-to-the-press-and-make-headlines-in-f1-2018 

Make Headlines in F1 2018 - out 24th August
